    "The test is considered a challenging benchmark for AI language models and is seen as a way to measure their ability to perform more advanced language tasks.4 https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theory_of_mind 5 An example question for probing commonsense: \"What are candles good for eliminating?",
    "Answer: Dark\".",
